The naming convention is a bit complex
If it's a single word, [hello]
Two or more, it's [HelloThere]
If it's a lib name, [Math]
Functions are [HelloThereHowAreYou & Hello]
One word built-ins are [hello]

This is a bit complex, and I need a standard
It needs to look decent..
Print doesn't looks good, but
Terminal.Print() does.
Temrinal.print() doesn't
It's complex.. Alone, a word looks bad upper case, with others, if every word is uppercase
it looks awesome

